{"tid":2401080,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[道歉文]對唔住大家，係我無小心保管波台聚會嘅合照","createTime":"2021-02-09T12:35:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-12T13:45:57.000Z","uid":96525,"like":336,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"e734ed47187bad756958fb1af6782d91b60923a2","tid":2401080,"uid":96525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T12:35:34.000Z","msg":"今日返返下工，feel到手機係咁震，比人炸signal先發現應該西將我哋聚會啲相貼咗上嚟<br />\n<br />\n令到好多波台手足受困擾，對唔住<br />\n<br />\n道歉名單如下:<br />\n1. N賓<br />\n2.逆插玫瑰<br />\n3.大雞樂<br />\n4.港毒之父<br />\n5.邱慧雯<br />\n6.佩雷斯主席<br />\n7.阿古路<br />\n8.范加爾<br />\n9.濕鳩lily<br />\n10.黑b<br />\n<br />\n除咗同你哋講對唔住<br />\n仲想多謝你哋送比我啲iPhone12(收到幾部)，iMac， LV手袋...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希望你哋唔好將呢單嘢入曼迷數，一人做事一人當當<br />\n今個post之後我會無限期退出波台，希望可以平息眾怒"},{"pid":"07146c4174e0c45b07b7e591ceb8808a1d0cd3e1","tid":2401080,"uid":1734,"like":59,"dislike":3,"score":56,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T12:37:08.000Z","msg":"我負責揸機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />對我無影響既"},{"pid":"394ba6283e3bfa9981f2904e32f10c056836d736","tid":2401080,"uid":2927,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T12:39:48.000Z","msg":"我bb 咁man 既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2898535a5858527913aa9347ee48fed4d98810e0","tid":2401080,"uid":13088,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"07146c4174e0c45b07b7e591ceb8808a1d0cd3e1","tid":2401080,"uid":1734,"like":59,"dislike":3,"score":56,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T12:37:08.000Z","msg":"我負責揸機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />對我無影響既"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T12:41:00.000Z","msg":"旗左"},{"pid":"1ff48f07564270568a908e71dc9875c512f45f33","tid":2401080,"uid":12628,"like":164,"dislike":3,"score":161,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T12:41:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.hkg